# browseVersions(_:)

**Instance Method**

Opens the Versions browser in the document’s main window.

## Declaration

```swift
@IBAction @MainActor func browseVersions(_ sender: Any?)
```

## Parameters

- **sender**: The control sending the message.

## Discussion

This is the action of the Browse Saved Versions menu item in a document-based app.

## Browsing Document Versions

- **isBrowsingVersions**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the document is currently displaying the Versions browser.
- **stopBrowsingVersions(completionHandler:)**: Dismiss the Versions browser for the current document.
